snippet.title: My Makeup Routine as a Waitress (chit chat grwm) | Amber Greaves
snippet.description:

My Bloopers Video!

hi guys!

i hope you enjoyed today's video where i show you my every day makeup routine as a waitress! i loved being able to just sit down and play with some makeup while also catching you guys up on where i've been. i'm so excited for all that is to come. 

Thanks again for watching!

xoxo,
Amber
